Challenge:

The Hawaiian tour company struggled to manage a growing volume of customer inquiries and lacked a 24/7 solution for answering questions and booking tours, leading to delays and missed opportunities.

Solution:

RomAIx built a custom AI chat assistant that provides real-time responses, offers personalized tour recommendations, and allows bookings directly from the chat window. The assistant supports multiple languages and integrates with the company's booking system.

Result:

The AI assistant reduced response times to 10 seconds, improved customer satisfaction by offering 24/7 support in any language, and streamlined the booking process, allowing the company to handle more inquiries efficiently.

AI-Powered Email Assistant - Supercharging Email Support with AI

Overview:

RomAIx developed an AI-powered email assistant for a tour company, designed to automate and enhance customer email responses. The assistant delivers fast, personalized replies, freeing up the support team to focus on more complex tasks while ensuring each interaction reflects the company’s unique brand and customer service values.

Email Agent

Challenge:

The tour company had to keep up with a high volume of daily customer inquiries, as staff spent too much time answering emails. This reduced efficiency and impacted their ability to handle other critical tasks, leading to slower response times and missed opportunities.

Solution:

We created an AI email assistant that processes incoming emails, drafts personalized responses in under 30 seconds, and integrates seamlessly with the company’s knowledge base. Live agents can review responses before they are sent, ensuring both accuracy and a personal touch.

Result:

With the AI email assistant, the company can now process over 100 emails per hour, significantly reducing response times and freeing up valuable time for the support team. This automation allows the company to handle higher volumes of inquiries, setting them up for future growth and scalability.

What is RomAIx?

RomAIx is an AI Automation Agency specializing in developing custom AI solutions such as virtual assistants and workflow automations to help businesses streamline their processes and improve efficiency.

What are custom AI assistants?

Custom AI assistants are AI tools designed to meet your business needs. RomAIx offers virtual assistants such as chatbots and AI voice assistants. That can be integrated into platforms such as your company's website but also social media platforms like Instagram and Facebook. RomAIx's AI assistants enhance efficiency, improve customer satisfaction, and provide scalable support tailored to your business needs.

What are automation workflows?

Automation workflows are systematic processes that use AI and software to perform tasks automatically. They help businesses reduce manual efforts, minimize errors, and increase productivity by automating repetitive tasks.

How does AI automation differ from traditional automation methods?

While traditional automation typically involves rule-based systems that follow predefined instructions, AI automation leverages artificial intelligence technologies such as machine learning and natural language processing to perform tasks intelligently and adapt to changing circumstances. This allows for more flexible and scalable automation solutions that can handle complex and unstructured data.
